===Proper noun===
'''[[天]][[命]]'''

#The doctrine of political [[legitimacy]] used by the kings of the [[Shang]] dynasty and by the Emperors of China. It asserts that Heaven would bless the reign of a just ruler, but would withdraw such a mandate if that ruler were to become unjust. Compare the [[Divine Right of Kings]].
#The first era name of the [[Qing]] Empire.

